description:
Cosmetic chemist Ni'kita Wilson drops mad scientist knowledge, including how to read an ingredient label, the truth about parabens, and which anti-aging creams are worth the money. Plus: Poetic justice for makeup, what to do if your face is allergic to exercise, and which foods cause acne.
